{"tid":2077260,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【網傳】北京平谷區秘密建立方艙醫院。每一步都是武漢翻版","createTime":"2020-06-24T06:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T05:21:17.000Z","uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"73fc990208cd6bc0f166f3ba3f40ac5b6bb394d8","tid":2077260,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"網上流傳文件顯示，北京平谷區肺炎防空辦公室6月20日決定，同意兩間醫院建立「方艙」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62OXdr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62OXdr2.jpg&h=20b4ec07&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n武漢疫情期間，因為醫院床位不足，為了收容輕症病人，而係體育館或展覽館臨時搭建床位。<br />\n武漢方艙：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHkeZ8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHkeZ8d.png&h=b3dcb0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：網上流傳，未經核實<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\nTwitter 戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1275636840188518403?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1275636840188518403%3Fs%3D20&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=6eff9792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1275636840188518403%3Fs%3D20&h=440b1a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1275636840188518403?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"e2cc009ca12ad439c8370a75344e26493e27899a","tid":2077260,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:59:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=8f798974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"29457f995ddfb8efb8597dfb1d63cbc23a476dd9","tid":2077260,"uid":274435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06